<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 01:22:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Winklevoss Twins 的 3.3 亿美元 Gemini 贷款在惨败后成为焦点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/winklevoss-twins-330-million-gemini-loans-in-focus-after-rout</link><description>由于加密货币交易所陷入财务困境，Gemini Space Station Inc. 今年已经损失了一半以上的市值，裁员 30%，并从主要海外市场撤出。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwXlxKM7K.BM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 19:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/winklevoss-twins-330-million-gemini-loans-in-focus-after-rout</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的加密货币机器发挥了新的杠杆作用</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/saylor-s-crypto-complex-powers-new-market-aiming-for-13-yield</link><description>迈克尔·塞勒策略公司(Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc.)首创的杠杆购买比特币模式催生了又一个与其命运相关的初创公司网络——如果比特币下跌，所有这些公司都会面临风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBhBvm3hSlPQ/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 16:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/saylor-s-crypto-complex-powers-new-market-aiming-for-13-yield</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行、渣打银行获得香港首张稳定币发行人牌照</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/hsbc-stanchart-get-first-hong-kong-stablecoin-issuer-licenses</link><description>香港已向汇丰控股有限公司和渣打银行的合资企业授予首张稳定币发行人许可证，使这两家银行成为首批发行与当地货币挂钩的加密货币的公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ir8YL2uPyTpQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 09:26:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-10/hsbc-stanchart-get-first-hong-kong-stablecoin-issuer-licenses</guid></item></channel></rss>